l/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d4f411cf6f5f6185c1b4c8cdd3dc3237eee6d7","tid":1949802,"uid":108512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:43:14.000Z","msg":"聽到個名都打冷震<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3483e673008af1e7801a1cc16d83fa260a161de1","tid":1949802,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:43:54.000Z","msg":"本港首宗市民違反檢疫令的案件，涉案男子被判入獄3個月。該男子居無定所，本月初經深圳灣口岸過關時申報假地址，兩日後打算離境探親，被當局揭發。男子今（30日）在粉嶺裁判法院，承認違反《若干到港人士強制檢疫規例》，被判囚3個月。庭上透露，他患有抑鬱症，新型冠狀病毒檢測結果呈陰性。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官判刑時稱，雖然被告成見恭介（Sing Kin Kung Kai，31歲）的病毒測試結果呈陰性，但病毒有潛伏期，無人能在檢測前確定自己沒有受感染；虛報地址乃罔顧公眾安全的自私行為，被告此舉白費了醫護的工夫，後果堪虞。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被告認罪後自行求情，表示從事外賣工作</span></span>，被捕至今已羈押多天，希望法庭判他守行為，「或者可唔可以交完罰款就走？」<br />\n<br />\n被告成見恭介的名字和足球動漫《踢出我天地》男主角原名一樣，他被控向獲授權人員提供虛假資料。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n換著背景係留學，會判坐3個月咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5ec720744fc165ca176be9e7b73298ed0d1899","tid":1949802,"uid":164368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7d7faa17237c85c2f6b183f63ef28de1bec77a83","tid":1949802,"uid":63113,"like":156,"dislike":2,"score":154,"quote":{"pid":"85957266434937a8257944d4025ab7305de95f1d","tid":1949802,"uid":28279,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T02:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />捉佢去通櫃！"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T02:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vOh4ZvA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvOh4ZvA.gif&h=ca69c538&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:45:22.000Z","msg":"龜呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2117e7a86ffbabc2567047435634c9159ff1bb65","tid":1949802,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislik